      "body" : "d89c332c597a1129aa9fd3293bd37e7ab90171eb\r\n\r\nCan't we refactor the test to remove these (LEAVE/ENTER)CRITICAL_SECTION? Looks like this block could go after `TestLoadWallet`?",
