      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "If I understand correctly, the `CheckLastCritical` call added by this commit in `LEAVE_CRITICAL_SECTION` should detect any inconsistent lock order without any modification on the lock stack.\r\n\r\nMaybe \"By checking lock order consistency (CheckLastCritical) before any unlocking (LeaveCritical) the lock tracking data must not have been broken by exception\"",
